---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';

const meta = {
  title: "Patient Information for AnaBella Family and Cosmetic Dentistry",
  description: "Download your new patient paperwork today. Or read about our financial and insurance policies. We are here to help.",
  canonical: "https://www.anabelladentistry.com/patient-information/",
};
---

<Layout title={meta.title} description={meta.description} canonical={meta.canonical}>
  <Header />
  <main class="interior-page">
    <div class="container interior-grid">
      <div class="interior-content">

        <h1>Patient Information</h1>

        <img
          class="page-hero-img"
          src="/assets/2017/01/woman-professional-staff-smiling.jpg"
          alt="AnaBella Family and Cosmetic Dentistry front desk staff"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />

        <h2>New Patient Paperwork</h2>

        <p><a href="/" class="text-link">AnaBella Family and Cosmetic Dentistry</a> offers our patient form(s) online so they can be completed in the convenience of your own home or office.</p>

        <ul>
          <li>All forms are PDF files. You will need AdobeReader® to view them.</li>
          <li>If you do not already have AdobeReader® installed on your computer, <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader/" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click Here</a> to download.</li>
          <li>Download the necessary form(s), print them out and fill in the required information.</li>
          <li>Bring the necessary form(s) to your appointment.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="pdf-list">
          <a href="/assets/forms/Patient-Information.pdf" class="pdf-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg class="pdf-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="#c1dbc7" />
              <path d="M13 2l4 4h-4V2z" fill="#72b7bc" />
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#72b7bc" stroke-width="1" />
              <text x="9" y="15" text-anchor="middle" font-size="5" font-weight="700" fill="#fff" font-family="sans-serif">PDF</text>
            </svg>
            <span class="pdf-info">
              <span class="pdf-name">Patient Registration</span>
              <span class="pdf-cta">Click to Download</span>
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="/assets/forms/Patient-Health-History.pdf" class="pdf-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg class="pdf-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="#c1dbc7" />
              <path d="M13 2l4 4h-4V2z" fill="#72b7bc" />
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#72b7bc" stroke-width="1" />
              <text x="9" y="15" text-anchor="middle" font-size="5" font-weight="700" fill="#fff" font-family="sans-serif">PDF</text>
            </svg>
            <span class="pdf-info">
              <span class="pdf-name">Health History Form</span>
              <span class="pdf-cta">Click to Download</span>
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="/assets/forms/Financial-Agreement.pdf" class="pdf-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg class="pdf-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="#c1dbc7" />
              <path d="M13 2l4 4h-4V2z" fill="#72b7bc" />
              <rect x="3" y="2" width="13" height="18" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#72b7bc" stroke-width="1" />
              <text x="9" y="15" text-anchor="middle" font-size="5" font-weight="700" fill="#fff" font-family="sans-serif">PDF</text>
            </svg>
            <span class="pdf-info">
              <span class="pdf-name">Financial Agreement</span>
              <span class="pdf-cta">Click to Download</span>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2>Financial Policy</h2>

        <p>We firmly believe that financial considerations should not be an obstacle to obtaining the treatment you desire. We are sensitive to the fact that each patient has different needs and have several payment options available so that treatment is accessible to everyone. All financial discussions and arrangements are kept strictly confidential.</p>

        <h2>Insurance Information</h2>

        <p>Dental insurance is diverse. Some policies cover only a small percentage of fees, while others cover 50 percent or greater. The more you or your employer pays for premiums, the better the coverage, in most cases. Dental insurance can be confusing, but we'll make it easy for you. Simply bring your card or claim into our office. We'll be happy to tell you what your insurance will cover and file your claim for you.</p>

      </div>
      <Sidebar />
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .interior-content ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }
  .interior-content ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .text-link {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .pdf-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .pdf-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .pdf-item:hover .pdf-name { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }
  .pdf-item:hover .pdf-cta  { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }

  .pdf-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .pdf-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .pdf-cta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
